<p>Time: 2023-02-23T07:00:00-05:00</p>
<p>Images: ['<a href="https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Santa-Barbara.jpg">Santa-Barbara.jpg</a>', '<a href="https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/sangre-y-cemento.jpg">sangre-y-cemento.jpg</a>']</p>
